’Ů@8d086cdc11fcc4e8e99f7e85ca2a9f5abe5733c8061c36b33b49a11a409705a7ŮőTitle: title: umask
Path: Examples
Content:
Print current default file creation permissions.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> umask


```
Make new files read-only to group and inaccessible to others.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> umask rwxr-x---


```
’Ů@5c5be2f84d4fc4fb5c4d7e25b68d7e543a6667ff63aa32f477933790744a60eaŮfTitle: title: umask
Path: Notes
Content:
When setting a new mask, the previous mask will be returned.
